  "title": "Is there any way to add user specific info to result of algolia?",
  "body": "Hi,\n\nI need to append some info related to authenticated user to the result returned by algolia algoliasearchHelper. I tried to make a ajax request inside helper.on method\n\n```\nhelper.on('result', function(data) {\n        renderHits(data);\n        myfunction(data);\n});\n```\n\nbut I always get this error: \"Uncaught TypeError: Illegal invocation\".\nDo you have any kind of suggestion?\n\nRegards\n",
